Package: timeseries.tools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Non-Stationary, Fractal, and Long Memory Time Series
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Emmanouil", "Mavrogiorgis",
                  email = "emm.n.black@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for analyzing time series exhibiting
    long-range dependence, non-stationarity, and fractal properties. Provides
    functions for Hurst-Kolmogorov process analysis, regime change detection,
    derivative pattern analysis, and simulation of fractional Brownian motion.
    Includes multiple methods for changepoint detection (variance, mean, trend,
    correlation) and nth-order derivative computation with regime identification.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/emm-n-m/persistance-nonstarionary-fractal-tools
